doppel.name: Doppel of Silence
doppel.title: Feature: Cuckoo
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is aware of how pitiful her Doppel is, and refuses to look at it. This Doppel wordlessly wraps around and strangles anything it doesn't want to hear as it continues its search for something to fill the hole in its heart. While it should be calling for someone, it is cowardly and afraid of acknowledging the reality it has concealed, and so it remains, silently covering its ears.

cardSkill.name: We're Together, We'll Be Fine
cardSkill.shortDescription: Heal [VIII] / ATK UP [VI] / Connecting with Yachiyo will restore some of her MP

chara.name: Iroha Tamaki
chara.description: Iroha came to Kamihama to investigate strange dreams she was having. Kind-hearted, she tends to worry too much about others. She's not up on the latest trends and isn't good with her phone. Usually reserved, she can be a fighter when it matters most.

charaMessageList.message: Is this what people call...bonds?

How long...since we've eaten out
as a family?

I lied to myself...
I didn't want them to dislike me.
Welcome back. I've been waiting for you.

I'm only interfering because you're so
precious to me!
I'm sorry... Your big sis is actually...

A little bitter… This taste brings back
such good memories.
Good thing I didn't give up!
I had faith that we'd be okay.
Your big sis did it!
Have I become a strong big sis?

chara.name: Iroha & Yachiyo
chara.title: Final Battle
chara.description: This Magical Girl pair was able to obtain a strength that supported them during a battle with an overwhelmingly strong Witch. Although they started off as enemies, they wound up becoming the best of friends, connected by an unbreakable bond. Their wings can only be seen the moment that power is ready.

charaMessageList.message: M-me?! But I've never modeled before!

This is back from when I used to work
in a modeling group.

If it's okay for us to just be
ourselves, then...

I can see how people would
think we're sisters.
We'll always be together...forever! Wink☆

It's been a while since I've felt
so excited for work.

This month is going to be tough
for Mikazuki Villa...
You really thought you could catch us off guard?
Our bond led us to victory, right?
"Are you okay, Yachiyo?" "Yes, I'm fine thanks to you."
"The feathers helped us win." "There's no more need for despair."

piece.description: In my many days of battle, I've seen countless sad sights, and endured just as many bitter moments... No matter what, I've resolved to live, so my past does not lose its meaning...

piece.description: I promised back then. That I would protect and save you. Even if that means I have to leap through time over and over again, I won't regret that choice. If there's enemies in the way, I won't hesitate to pull the trigger. Wait for me, Madoka... I'll change fate for you!

piece.description: Stars scattered throughout the cosmos, lend me your strength! (SPAAARKLEEE!) Here it goooes! I'm sending the power of the Cancer Zodiac into the heavens! I am an avatar of courage that pinches all things! (SHIIIIIING!) Mado...KANCEEEEEEEEER!

pieceSkill.name: Sunset Glow [IX]
pieceSkill.shortDescription: Negate Bewitch Chance [IX] / Blast Damage UP [II]

piece.description: The last ray of sunlight dyes the summer sky crimson, but it's the dark blue sky that follows that ends the day. The breeze running through my hair, and the sweet sound of the ocean... The view I lost myself in during that moment was a treasure more valuable than any other.
